    y 2v "我对她的写作风格没有什么特别的兴趣..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_4_afb52001:


    y "只是按照她的要求做了。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_4_e45b137d:


    y "不过..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_4_c68d2702:


    y 1s "好吧，我觉得偶尔写写简单的东西也没那么糟。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_4_79454ffe:


    y 1m "它可以让人耳目一新，你懂吗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_4_5d1bb453:


    y "可以让我偶尔平静一下我的思绪。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_4_9d91c067:


    mc "嗯...我同意。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_4_aa50b32a:


    mc "谢谢你的分享。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_2a706aa2:


    "在读完诗后，我想把它还给優里。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_00650c09:


    "不过她并没有接过去，而是看向了一边。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_71a86863:


    y "..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_41745b04:


    y "你是...不喜欢吗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_9dc95788:


    mc "啊--不，当然不是。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_0c90f7c0:


    mc "我只是...不知道自己应该怎么回应。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_967ce531:


    "虽然優里的诗通常都有些晦涩，但是想要理解这首诗并不难。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_40da8714:


    "而且，这显然不是夏树说她写的内容..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_bacefe7d:


    "...也就是说，我可能是她唯一展示过那首诗的人。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_66a66311:


    y 2v "我-我不知道自己能不能解释清楚这首诗..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_d969f247:


    mc "没关系。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_693b3366:


    mc "我能理解这首。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_778bbd0d:


    y 4c "..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_0d32b932:


    "優里现在说起话来比平时还要困难。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_9af5ef03:


    mc "这首诗...对你很重要吗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_c588c8d6:


    "優里点了点头。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_b88f0f95:


    mc "我不是很擅长言辞，不过..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_b39d66df:


    mc "很高兴你能和我分享。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_5ad4095e:


    mc "所以，谢谢你。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_dc89fda3:


    mc "希望我们还能一起共度时光。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_db13f9fb:


    "尽管我无法进行眼神接触，但我还是看到了優里唇边浮现了淡淡的微笑。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_81bfeaf4:


    "我又一次试着把诗还给她。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_c137d0ec:


    "但是優里轻轻地抓住我的手、推回到我的身上。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_5df5fce4:


    "我不知道该对她那温暖的触碰做出怎样的回应。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_3373ed73:


    y 1v "你可以..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_a1300026:


    y "唔..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_24b12ec4:


    y "这首诗..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_e570a115:


    "優里又一次无法完整地组织起一句话。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_84847dff:


    mc "你是说我可以留着它？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_c588c8d6_1:


    "優里点了点头。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_8b8a764a:


    mc "我很乐意。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_569c5de3:


    "優里又淡淡地微笑了起来，似乎不想让我注意到。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_3962c4bd:


    y "你总是.."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_b41f1bcf:


    y "你总是...让我感觉很好。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_44f10fda:


    y "我知道我不擅长和人打交道，不过..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_a0352924:


    y "我希望...自己有些时候能回报一下。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_cf1adef2:


    mc "嗯。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_94d64b74:


    mc "别担心。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_0c64be78:


    mc "我觉得你做得挺好的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_cfa2b519:


    "優里终于转过身面对着我。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_4454245f:


    y 1s "我想...在莫妮卡说话前，我们得进行下一步了。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_e3f8b2c9:


    y "不过我们之后肯定能再聊聊的..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_cf1adef2_1:


    mc "是的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_fed264ae:


    mc "一定会的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_5_d486bdfc:


    "就这样，優里羞怯地对我笑了笑，而我回到了座位上，将她的诗收了起来。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_8bc60d0a:


    n 2q "嗯..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_142c173a:


    n "我说了你不会喜欢的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_d3dee951:


    mc "我喜欢。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_34480524:


    n 2h "什么？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_a21b5078:


    n "说实话！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_21d60d8b:


    mc "我确实喜欢。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_ecb80d6e:


    mc "我为什么你这么确信我不会喜欢呢？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_5ac436cf:


    n 5w "好吧--"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_a0fd7848:


    n "因为！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_1c679434:


    n "高中里的所有人都认为，文章应该的复杂丰满的..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_b0362bb0:


    n 5q "所以大家都不把我的文章当回事。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_37bb2ed8:


    mc "但是，诗的关键不就是要表达自己吗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_1037df30:


    mc "你的写作风格并不会使主旨逊色一分。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_e590aff4:


    n 1k "是的！就是这样！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_07c4c67c:


    n "我喜欢那些读起来容易，但是又能狠狠触动你的诗。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_4953d883:


    n 1c "就像这首诗一样。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_eb023f69:


    n "看着身边的所有人都在做大事，这真是让人沮丧啊..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_856d9a9c:


    n "所以我就决定将它写下来。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_17bdd5f5:


    mc "嗯，我能理解。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_2d5e407c:


    n 2a "不过简单地写作还有一个好处，它可以更注重文字游戏。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_b7bddf1e:


    n "比如说，我在每句话末尾设置了韵脚，但随即就押错韵。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_30b4c81a:


    n "这样就可以帮助我从上一行中的情绪中摆脱出来。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_2e7cfcfe:


    mc "所以你这么做..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_cbc76093:


    mc "似乎比我意识到的还要更深入一些。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_3e80a161:


    n 4y "这就是专业！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_d399c51a:


    n "很高兴你能学到些东西。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_cb6fa18b:


    n "你没想到会从年纪最小的人这里学到吧？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_e94aacb9:


    mc "是啊...没想到过。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_fb5f7062:


    "我决定就这样迁就她一次。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_6_87970ac1:


    "我其实并不在意大家的年纪，不过如果夏树对此感到自豪的话，那么我也不会说破的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_dd108a9d:


    n 2a "还不错，是吧？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_60187f07:


    mc "比起昨天那首要长多了。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_eb02eb50:


    n 2w "昨天那首太短了..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_3f4cc55b:


    n "我只是热热身而已！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_d1347742:


    n 2c "希望你不会误以为那是我的上限。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_9b943f22:


    mc "不，当然不会..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_ae8ffbf5:


    n 2a "不管怎么说，这首诗的主旨还是相当直白的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_038f9631:


    n "我都怀疑需不需要我来解释。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_b1f57678:


    n 2c "有时候你可以用简单的类比来解释复杂的事情..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_3172d35d:


    n "而且这样可以让大家意识到他们一直以来有多笨了。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_d97a6e91:


    n 2g "比如说，所有人都会认同这首诗的主题是一个愚昧的混蛋..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_83e5c791:


    mc "你认识这样的人吗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_b5672bed:


    n 2c "当然啦。这首诗就是关于大家怎么看待我的--"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_c7bb1f66:


    n 5w "...这无关紧要！关于什么都行！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_585f6446:


    n 5h "我写它是为了容易联系起..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_81bb56c3:


    n "所有人都会有某种古怪的爱好，或者说是一种带有负罪感的快乐。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_ff0627ba:


    n 5q "某种你害怕别人发现、并且因此取笑或是看轻你的东西。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_a24ab514:


    n 1e "...但这只会让人变得愚蠢！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_0a24a428:


    n "只要他们没有伤害到任何人，并且从中得到了快乐，谁会在乎他们喜欢什么呢？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_89f0d418:


    n 1q "我觉得人们真的需要学会尊重他人的古怪爱好..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_5b1ae15d:


    mc "唔，很有意思..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_d1065305:


    mc "優里今天也写了类似的东西。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_00a51a21:


    n 1h "嗯？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_dbe127d0:


    n "你刚刚说了優里？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_69c25b65:


    mc "是啊..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_ed23577e:


    mc "她说她的诗是关于自己的一个不寻常的爱好。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_f7ab9610:


    mc "我不是很能理解，不过她说的跟你差不多..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_a403e768:


    mc "人们不应该让彼此因为这些而感到不安。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_9bdce4df:


    n 1q "真的吗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_228e3b68:


    n "好吧..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_6fbb1460:


    n 1t "我是说，優里挺古怪的，所以我也毫不怀疑她会有些古怪的爱好..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_5437b16a:


    n "...而不是说这样有什么不对！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_84b5aa9d:


    n 1u "唔..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_6c4b6440:


    n "我并不是...评判她什么的..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_6095f763:


    "夏树不知道该说什么。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_0f2ba2e6:


    n 1q "我-我想我应该试试，不要那么刻薄地对她..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_dbe057d9:


    n "既然她对于自己的古怪行为感到不安的话..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_37e21fa0:


    n "我是说，我很讨厌那些让我觉得不安的人..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_db0decad:


    n 1w "而優里昨天就让我觉得不安了！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_96a143b0:


    n 1s "不过从你说的话来看，她似乎已经吸取教训了..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_c8200692:


    mc "是的，我也这么觉得。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_005bbbce:


    mc "即便她的写作风格和你大不相同，我也敢肯定地说，她会喜欢你诗里的主旨的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_15d04663:


    mc "嗯，你说得没错。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_5c3fc08d:


    mc "至少我可以联想到。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_e4b24602:


    mc "而且我相信很多人也可以。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_cb52b8b3:


    n 4h "那个..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_1b4d30d3:


    n "我很高兴你能欣赏这类文字..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_01b8854b:


    n 4q "我是说...我知道我昨天已经说过了。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_ea6ff1f9:


    n "不过我一直...嗯，我一直都很享受和你分享我的文字，所以..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_da826cb1:


    n 4w "...所以你就想想自己有多幸运吧，好吗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_ee7d9dbd:


    mc "啊哈哈。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_30f93a8f:


    mc "好啦，谢谢你的坦诚。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_fe3d9171:


    n 1n "你这么说是什么意思？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_4989bca6:


    n "我一直都很坦诚的！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_afb600b7:


    n 12b "天哪..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_07b7c0fd:


    n "你也期待一下明天，可以吗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_fd5f8bbc:


    mc "好的，我会的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_df407eec:


    n 4c "毕竟那是我最擅长的！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_2dfb5cb0:


    n "除非能从中传递出一个好的主旨，不然我都不喜欢写作。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_ea30310f:


    n "比如说，传递情绪很重要..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_8c60d0ad:


    n "但是我想要让人们思考，而不是单纯地感受。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_d2d33a6f:


    n 4b "记住这点！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_7_551f7269:


    n "我也会为明天写一首好诗的，所以敬请期待。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_414b5f0c:


    n 2a "嗯..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_a8d27ddf:


    n "我感觉自己一直在写消极的东西，所以我这次想要写点有积极意义的东西。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_badae2c6:


    n 2z "况且...沙滩太棒了！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_d4849c6b:


    n 2j "很难写出关于沙滩的消极内容。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_fcf484f2:


    mc "所以你是先决定写沙滩，然后再想出主旨的？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_d9e61fcc:


    n 2c "嗯，是的..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_ff427fc5:


    n "只是因为昨天发生的事情。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_a898b508:


    n 5q "我是说，在優里和我意识到我们写了同一件东西的时候..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_9c8cb24c:


    n "她想挑一个主题，让我们俩都写它，差不多就这样。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_a7bcf340:


    mc "我明白了..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_c5c52c14:


    "由此可知，優里给我看的那首诗，并不是她打算给其他人看的那首..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_7a8c5a9c:


    "当然，我选择对夏树进行了隐瞒。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_c722c4b2:


    mc "好吧，優里处理地更严肃一点。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_3355af86:


    n 5h "嗯，那--"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_e897feb4:


    n 42c "天哪...她最好没有说我的坏话！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_d19ef80f:


    n "毕竟是她想让我们写同一个主题的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_4e355357:


    n 1s "呃...你也能看出这是她要求的吧。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_415f6d11:


    n "让我们两个写同一个主题，然后试图用一些花哨的东西打动我。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_68618747:


    n 1w "好吧，其实我并不在乎。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_a70f6259:


    n "我只是这么做了而已。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_11801a2a:


    n 1q "我是说，我觉得我的诗最后也有些隐喻..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_2b3a7296:


    n "...不过偶尔这么做也没什么问题啊！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_8_2221c3bc:


    n "至少这是也一次不错的练习。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_e9173862:


    n 1q "..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_e6529392:


    n "...为什么你要那样看着我？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_1825e66c:


    n "如果你不喜欢，那你就说出来。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_0342295b:


    n 1u "我不会...生气的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_69e4e05c:


    mc "不，我不是不喜欢它...！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_1a40fb94:


    mc "它只是...读起来有些让人惊讶。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_83b6981f:


    "这首诗显然不是優里告诉我的那首..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_bacefe7d:


    "...也就是说，我可能是看过这首诗的人。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_ea8aa9a8:


    mc "呃...我觉得我只是还不习惯从你身上听到这样的好话..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_f9917ed7:


    n 1h "别-别那么说！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_a26aa930:


    n 1n "笨蛋..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_50b8fc71:


    n "你觉得...写作的意义是什么？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_667815e2:


    n 1u "表达你无法说出来的东西..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_8f04ea9e:


    mc "是的...我能理解。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_c9fcaaa9:


    mc "很抱歉，有时候我会忽略重点。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_2ea97b1b:


    mc "我的本意是好的..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_9563dbe7:


    mc "而且...我很高兴你能把它拿给我看。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_8dec91ad:


    mc "我很喜欢。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_aaeb54a0:


    n 1h "好吧...嗯..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_faf3284b:


    n 1q "我...我是专业的，所以..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_a230e7fc:


    "夏树嘟囔着，完全不像她平时自信的样子。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_527e1928:


    n "一定要..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_66d32072:


    n 12c "你给我记得...有时候我也会思考这些东西！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_f4d23eb0:


    n "你知道的，当你对我好的时候，它..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_3aeee00a:


    n 12a "..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_33cc570e:


    n "...很有意义。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_df93c20f:


    mc "啊...我很高兴。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_6e96852a:


    "感觉到夏树满意了之后，我想把诗还给她。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_d33d2ed4:


    "但当我这么做时，夏树抓住了我的手、推回到我的身上。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_f19a9b83:


    "她那又小又软的手坚决得让我吃惊。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_0ff74f7f:


    n 12b "我不要。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_bbe4458e:


    mc "诶...？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_56c3991c:


    mc "为什么？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_185521b7:


    n 12c "我就是不要！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_a8557d5c:


    n "天哪..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_9a0675d7:


    "我意识到了夏树在做什么。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_5ecdadf6:


    "她做不到坦诚，所以只好用迂回的手段，试图把诗交给我。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_00801b73:


    mc "好吧...这样的话，那我就收下了。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_aedc0f57:


    "我没有调侃她，而是选择了照做。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_c27d8493:


    n 1t "...很好。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_552ff42d:


    n "如果你不这么做的话，我会..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_bb2cf764:


    n "..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_b5e34640:


    n 1h "算了..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_a506398c:


    n 1q "我只是...很高兴你会收下它。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_3cd314cd:


    "夏树欲言又止地只说到了这里。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_b62c10bb:


    "尽管她已经尽力隐藏自己的表情了，但我还能看到她淡淡地微笑了起来。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_842a5d0d:


    n "就这样吧，那么..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_0f718df6:


    n 1s "在别人看到之前把它收起来，好吗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_21d5c9ec:


    mc "啊...好的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_22b3e162:


    mc "我会的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_9_e099d11a:


    "就这样，我回到了自己的座位上，将夏树的诗收了起来。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_e87e0575:


    mc "紗世里..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_c878179c:


    mc "我只是猜想了一下，不过..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_ee942d6f:


    mc "你是不是到了今天早上才写了这首诗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_c7a4af52:


    s 4h "不是！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_659f3f9f:


    s 4l "只-只有一点！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_117ad0c7:


    mc "你不能对一个是或否的问题回答'只有一点'..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_3ec02b40:


    s 5b "我昨晚忘了写..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_1ef71577:


    mc "好吧，至少这让我的自我感觉好了些..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_7794a4fa:


    s 1h "不要这么刻薄！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_66e312d4:


    s "我还是尽力了..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_d080b42e:


    mc "啊，好吧..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_74f745b3:


    mc "我不是说这首诗不好。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_a42d9969:


    mc "结果还不错...嗯，该怎么说好呢..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_6eea2305:


    mc "这很紗世里。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_e99aeedf:


    s 1d "真的吗？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_cf1adef2:


    mc "是的。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_5b9eafb1:


    mc "尤其是最后一行..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_513164ac:


    s 4r "我做了鸡蛋和烤面包！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_9fbed175:


    mc "即便你上学要迟到了...？"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_53229aa9:


    s 5d "不吃早饭是不好的！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_ed9a7c92:


    s "我会感觉不安的..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_3748b1c9:


    mc "好吧，我觉得这样争论没什么意义..."


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_b9610080:


    mc "不管怎么样，谢谢你能给我看这首诗。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_4fe8273d:


    s 1q "诶嘿嘿～"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_3dbfe6ed:


    s "真是太有意思了。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_6eddcdae:


    s "莫妮卡是最棒的！"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_21d5c9ec:


    mc "啊...是啊。"


translate chinese _call_showpoem_10_6f0fbb10:


